  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Fluorinated gases and ozone-depleting substances: how to do business if there's a no-deal Brexit
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">How businesses can continue to trade and deal in fluorinated greenhouse gases and ozone-depleting substances in the UK and EU if there's a no-deal Brexit.</p>

  </div>
</div>

